# Welcome

This is your first post. Write it in Markdown right here on GitHub — no special editor needed.

## What you can do

- **Bold** and *italic* text
- Lists like this one
- `inline code` and full code blocks
- Blockquotes

> "Writing is thinking. To write well is to think clearly." — David McCullough

## A code block example

```python
def hello():
    print("Hello from my blog!")
```

## Wrap up

Delete this file and add your own posts to the `posts/` folder. Each one needs the frontmatter at the top (the block between the `---` lines).

To mark a post as **featured**, add `featured: true` to its frontmatter. Only one post should have this at a time.
